properties.sfomuseum:author: United Kingdom Air Ministry
properties.sfomuseum:description: 35 page brown paper cover with interior clasp binding containing looseleaf sheets of paper. Contents: Authorisation of Flights /Duties of Captain, Starting Up, Crew Responsibilities Before Departure, Wearing Parachutes, Safety Belts and Harnesses, Responsibilities of Crews in Normal Flight, Special Responsibilities of Crews in Cross Country Flights, Avoidance of Areas, Special Responsibilities of Crews in Armament or Fighting Training, Special Responsibilities of Pilots / Aerobatics, Responsibilities of Crews in Landings, Restrictions, Regulations for Bad Visibility Conditions.
